M - Serla sees better earnings prospect 97 . Finnish forest industry group Metsa - Serla Oy president and CEO Jorma Vaajoki said on Thursday he expected the prospects for 1997 earnings to be slightly better than this year . " It looks like next year ' s earnings level and the possibilities to achieve earnings would be slightly better than this year , " Vaajoki told reporters after a news conference . Metsa - Serla earlier reported a sharp fall in January - August profits , and said it expected to post a loss in the final tertial , but the full - year 1996 result would nevertheless show a profit . Vaajoki said Metsa - Serla ' s 1996 result would be " clearly positive " . He did not elaborate . - - Helsinki Newsroom + 358 - 9 - 680 50 245 
